  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "On a lightly floured surface, roll out the puff pastry to a thickness of 1/8 inch.",
    "Transfer the pastry to a 9x13 inch baking dish.",
    "Arrange the mixed greens, cherry tomatoes, and red onion in a single layer on top of the pastry.",
    "Sprinkle the feta cheese and fresh oregano over the top of the vegetables.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Bake the bresaola in the preheated oven for 25 minutes, or until golden brown.",
    "Remove the bresaola from the oven and let it cool for 10 minutes.",
    "Serve warm, garnished with additional oregano if desired."
  ],
